const qBank = [
    {

       "question": "What is the scientific name of bitterfly?",
       "answers":[
       "Apis",
       "Coleoptrea",
       "Formicidae",
       "Rhopalocera"
   ],
       "correctIndex": 3
},

{

    "answers":[
        "1,233K",
        "5,778K",

        "101,300K"

    "correctIndex" : 1
}, 

{

},

{

},

    "correctIndex": 0
},

{
    "Id": "8",

    "correctIndex":2
},

{

},

{
    "Id": "10",

    "answers":[

        "7,918ft",
        "19,341ft",

    "correctIndex":1
},

{
    "Id": "11",

    "answers":[
        "May 2, 2008",
        "May 4, 2012",
        "May 3, 2013",
        "April 4, 2014",
    ],
    "correctIndex": 1
},

{
    "Id": "12",
    "question": "What is 48,879 in hexidecimal?",
    "answers":[
        "0x18C1",
        "0xBEEF",
        "0xDEAD",
        "0x12D591"
    ],
    "correctIndex":1
}

]


export default(n = 5) => Promise.resolve(qBank.sort(() => 0.5 - Math.random()).slice(0, n));
